                "created_at": "2022-11-06T00:00:00.000Z",
                "note": "<p>My <a href=\"https://mastodon.nl/tags/cats\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>cats</span></a> don't mind I am quite solitary. I am not against humans, just not always comfortable: I prefer being with 1 than in a crowd although occasional parties: \ud83d\ude0a\ud83d\udc83</p><p>I often care a lot, especially about <a href=\"https://mastodon.nl/tags/animals\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>animals</span></a> &amp; <a href=\"https://mastodon.nl/tags/nature\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>nature</span></a>, and often forget Poe's law.</p><p>Teacher &amp; writer of <a href=\"https://mastodon.nl/tags/Adobe\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Adobe</span></a> software books, my banners are my work.<br>I speak English Dutch French German &amp; Cat. Swarovski ring, unobtainium heart.</p><p>To avoid weirdness I use follow requests \ud83d\ude0a</p><p><a href=\"https://mastodon.nl/tags/science\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>science</span></a> <a href=\"https://mastodon.nl/tags/facts\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>facts</span></a> <a href=\"https://mastodon.nl/tags/design\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>design</span></a> <a href=\"https://mastodon.nl/tags/scifi\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>scifi</span></a> (Babylon 5, Star Trek)</p>",
